  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Storekeeper",
  "description": "<h3><strong>5 days work week, base on rostering (44 hours per week)</strong></h3>\n<h3><br></h3>\n<h3><strong>Primary Responsibility</strong></h3>\n<p>The Storekeeper plays a critical role in supporting store operations by managing inventory flow, ensuring accurate stock handling, and maintaining an organized and efficient back-of-house environment. This role helps ensure that merchandise is readily available for replenishment and that the store operates smoothly behind the scenes.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Inventory Management &amp; Storekeeping</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Receive, check, and verify incoming stock against delivery orders or invoices.</li>\n  <li>Replenish merchandise on sales floors in a timely and accurate manner based on store needs.</li>\n  <li>Pack, tag, and sort merchandise for storage or display according to standard procedures.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with warehouse and logistics teams to ensure smooth and timely deliveries.</li>\n  <li>Maintain proper stock organization in both the storeroom and sales floor.</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular stock counts and assist in inventory audits as required.</li>\n  <li>Report discrepancies, damages, or inventory issues to the store leadership team promptly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Housekeeping &amp; Safety</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure cleanliness and tidiness in the storeroom and back-of-house areas at all times.</li>\n  <li>Dispose of packaging waste and materials (cartons, wrappers, plastics) responsibly.</li>\n  <li>Comply with workplace safety, security, and housekeeping standards to maintain a hazard-free environment.</li>\n  <li>Ensure safe handling of goods and assist in lifting or moving stock where required.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Singaporean/SPR preferred</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in a stockroom or warehouse role is preferred but not mandatory.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and comfortable with manual handling and lifting.</li>\n  <li>Good organizational skills and attention to detail.</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of inventory systems and retail operations is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Team player with a positive attitude and strong sense of responsibility.</li>\n</ul>",
